question:
When I add up the last 2 check expects by hand I get different results than the given check-expects
Can anyone confirm that these check-expects are correct? I don't see any path that results in the given value.
student_answer:
All are possible. Please note that the problem statement says: 
;; This function
;; produces the total duration of the routes followed as soon as it finds a
;; treasure labeled s.
Meaning, the fastest route is not always the one travelled. There is some long way around that gets to the treasure labeled s.
